WORKOUT DETAILS
⏱️ Duration: 20 minute
🏋️ Equipment: A non-slip workout mat
⏱️ Intervals: 45 seconds work, 15 seconds rest

Exercises for this no repeat, no equipment full body HIIT workout:

00:00 Get Ready!
00:15 Air Squats
01:15 Pop Squats
02:15 3X Squat Pulse + Jump
03:30 Side to Side Squats
04:30 Squat to Curtsy Lunge
05:30 Sumo Squats
06:45 Burpees
07:45 Mountain Climbers
08:45 High Knees

11:00 Plank Shoulder Taps
12:00 Plank Up Downs
13:15 W Supermans
14:15 Bear Squat Push Ups
15:15 Superman Lat Pull Down
16:30 Leg Lifts
17:30 Cross Toe Touches
